<subSubSection id="7B860409E311E89DBCE3E464FE440592" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="D3E89204BABAFBEB27FD27A6C331A5C4" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0F7C9482D48FE38243FE9C0F9E3C0E00" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Mexico (Puebla, Veracruz) in disturbed broadleaved cloud forest and oak forest, in shady canyons and on mountainsides, 1250-1450 m in elevation (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="1DFCD86CBD7CF43768A3F7AB741C2B5E" captionStart="Figure 111" captionStartId="F111" captionText="Figure 111. Map of geographic distribution of L. venturana based on herbarium specimen data." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.168.51904.figure111" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/480125" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">111</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption id="17EA48A20880CCBCCBF15A3557FF4B30" doi="10.3897/phytokeys.168.51904.figure111" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/480125" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" start="Figure 111" startId="F111">
